<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 12:32:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>石油价格预示风险，加密货币交易者提心吊胆</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-traders-on-tenterhooks-as-oil-prices-signal-risks</link><description>随着美国市场在中东爆炸事件后重新开放，数字资产交易谨慎，交易员关注石油、股票和货币的连锁反应。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/irLFdjIcn3HI/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 03:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-02/crypto-traders-on-tenterhooks-as-oil-prices-signal-risks</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击引发不确定性，加密货币面临压力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-01/bitcoin-btc-recovery-looks-tepid-as-iran-strikes-stir-uncertainty</link><description>周末美国和以色列对伊朗的袭击动摇了投资者的信心，导致加密货币面临压力，交易者等待全球传统市场的指示。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9yiM3Ul6pt0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 07:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-01/bitcoin-btc-recovery-looks-tepid-as-iran-strikes-stir-uncertainty</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 伊朗赌注达 5.29 亿美元，新钱包大获全胜</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/polymarket-iran-bets-hit-529-million-as-new-wallets-draw-notice</link><description>随着本周末美国和以色列的炸弹落在伊朗身上，Polymarket 上的投注者（其中与袭击时间相关的合同交易额达 5.29 亿美元）开始获利。区块链侦探几乎立即开始在最近的投注中寻找不寻常的模式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.fUiA15VPBE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 21:24:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/polymarket-iran-bets-hit-529-million-as-new-wallets-draw-notice</guid></item><item><title>伊朗领导人去世后比特币恢复至 68,000 美元以上</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</link><description>在伊朗证实该国最高领导人在美国和以色列的军事行动中被杀后，比特币和其他加密货币在周日亚洲早盘交易中大幅反弹。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivFEZEB6t.QU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 07:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</guid></item></channel></rss>